==Vandalic==
===Etymology===
From Proto-Germanic *''hailaz'' "whole, healthy", from Proto-Indo-European *''kailos''.
===Interjection===
'''eils'''

# [[hail|Hail]]!
===Quotations===
*'''c390,''' ''De conviviis barbaris''
*:Inter '''''eils''''' Goticum ''scapia matzia ia drincan''
*:non audet quisquam dignos educere versus.
